tika.dc.description: Through guided meditations, simple rituals, awareness exercises, chakra work, and the principles of inner alchemy, Gee teaches you how to strengthen your intuitive power to enhance and maintain emotional and physical health. She shows you how to useyour intuition to guide you through life and provide guidance for others. Illustrated. Reading list. Index.
